creator: richlv@nakts.net
text:
in https://httpd.apache.org/docs/current/mod/mod_ssl.html#sslproxyengine , there's a sentence like this :

Note that the SSLProxyEngine directive should not, in general, be included in a virtual host that will be acting as a forward proxy (using <Proxy> or <ProxyRequest> directives.

looks like the closing parenthesis is missing at the end of the sentence.
